<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb52be26a-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s488i/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> $2,000,000 for fiscal year 2008; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb52be26b-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s488i/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> $10,750,000 for each of fiscal years 2009 through 2012.</content>
</paragraph>
